#load 52 weeks data

dataPath<-"C:/Users/FKH/Desktop/MScA/MSCA 31006 Time Series Analysis and Forecasting/Project"
data<-read.csv(paste(dataPath,'hungary_chickenpox2.csv',sep = '/'), header=TRUE)
row.names(data)<-data$Date
Date<-data$Date
data<-data[-1]
data$TOTAL<-rowSums(data)
total<-ts(data$TOTAL,frequency=52,start=c(2005,1))

Plot total data

plot(total)

KPSS test for total

kpss.test(total)
## 
##  KPSS Test for Level Stationarity
## 
## data:  total
## KPSS Level = 0.67695, Truncation lag parameter = 6, p-value = 0.01564

Transformation

#natural log
lambda<-0
trans.total<-BoxCox(total,lambda)
plot(trans.total)

KPSS test for trans total

kpss.test(trans.total)
